HEADWORD: Taleteller
<hw>Tale"tell`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who tells
tales or stories, especially in a mischievous or officious manner; a
talebearer; a telltale; a tattler.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

